snippet: Novak Djokovic, Rafael Nadal and Serena Williams barely got their shoes dusty at the French Open on Tuesday but two of the top five women's seeds went out and Andy Murray survived the first round by the skin of his teeth....
lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic, Rafael Nadal and Serena Williams barely got their shoes dusty at the French Open on Tuesday but two of the top five women's seeds went out and Andy Murray survived the first round by the skin of his teeth.

headline.print_headline: Easy for Djokovic and Nadal, Murray Suffers, Kerber Out
headline.main: Easy for Djokovic and Nadal, Murray Suffers, Kerber Out
